Thank you very much for purchasing \C[14]Luna~NTR Dungeon
Debt Repayment Life~\C[0].
First, let me explain how to operate the game.

～Keyboard Controls～. Switch message window with
'\C[2]Shift\C[0]'. Fast-forward messages with
'\C[2]Ctrl\C[0]', '\C[2]W\C[0]', '\C[2]Alt\C[0]'. Backlog
with '\C[2]Q\C[0]'.

～Mouse Controls～. Left click for
'\C[2]Confirm\C[0].\C[2]Character Movement\C[0]'. Right
click for '\C[2]Menu
Screen\C[0].\C[2]Cancel\C[0].\C[2]Message Screen
Toggle\C[0]'. Scroll wheel up \C[2]↑\C[0] for
'\C[2]Backlog\C[0]' and down \C[2]↓\C[0] for '\C[2]Message
Progress\C[0]'.

Please be aware that rapid use of the "Fast-forward
Messages" function during animations may occasionally result
in display errors.

There are flashing effects in H-scenes and others, so we
recommend playing in a well-lit room.
Please set the name of Luna's \C[2]boyfriend\C[0].

Would you like to watch the opening? (Approximately 10
minutes)
いいえ(スキップ三行説明)\B[4]

The protagonist \C[2]Luna\C[0]'s boyfriend \C[2]Taro\C[0] is
forced into monster hunting to repay a debt of \C[17]10
million G\C[0] in interest charged by an unscrupulous
trading company. They head to a solitary island with a
\C[3]Tower Dungeon\C[0], where four men who set their sights
on Luna await, and thus begins their isolated island life to
repay the debt.
The 【Taro Kiss】 reminiscence scene has been added.
